    "description": "<strong>严酷的现实，逝去的热情。</strong><br><strong>这是一个关于两名游戏创作者的故事。</strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >概要</h2>程式设计师蟹井和画师熊手是在专科学校认识的好朋友。<br>毕业之后，两人为了合力创作游戏，决定不找特定的工作，但现实生活并没有那么简单。<br>他们的游戏销量不佳，为了维持生计，大部分时间都浪费在打工兼差上……<br><br><br>就在蟹井绞尽脑汁，试图创造出能够畅销的产品时，熊手做出了一个决定——<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >游戏介绍</h2>《GOODBYE WORLD》是一款偏重剧情的冒险游戏。<br>玩家将要挑战包含12个关卡的平台解谜游戏，同时体验两位主角共计13个章节的故事。<br>（剧情为单线故事，没有多重结局。）<br><br><br>13章像素风视觉小说，伴随Olduct制作的原创音乐，讲述有关梦想、挣扎、自我追寻的故事。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1833490/extras/2dcc46366aa770f64cffe130b4baedfa.poster.avif?t=1725002803\" width=600 height=330 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1833490/extras/2dcc46366aa770f64cffe130b4baedfa.webm?t=1725002803\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1833490/extras/2dcc46366aa770f64cffe130b4baedfa.mp4?t=1725002803\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><br>在平台解谜游戏“BlOCKS”的12个关卡中避开危险、取得砖块、铺就平台、寻找钥匙，打开通关之门。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1833490/extras/12a920d7e8bc9bab2ae1906944d26c19.poster.avif?t=1725002803\" width=600 height=330 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1833490/extras/12a920d7e8bc9bab2ae1906944d26c19.webm?t=1725002803\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1833490/extras/12a920d7e8bc9bab2ae1906944d26c19.mp4?t=1725002803\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > 角色介绍 </h2><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1833490/extras/cc93659841a3bbad4ddf315521d06b8c.avif?t=1725002803\" width=